  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, you gain&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Darkvision\">darkvision</a>&nbsp;with a range of up to 30 feet. If you already have&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Darkvision\">darkvision</a>, its range instead increases by 30 feet. At 9th level, you gain&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/universal-monster-rules#TOC-Lifesense-Su-\">lifesense</a>&nbsp;with a range of 30 feet (<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/universal-monster-rules#TOC-Lifesense-Su-\">lifesense</a>&nbsp;allows you to sense and locate living creatures as if you had the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Blindsight-and-Blindsense\">blindsight</a>&nbsp;ability).</p>"
